These shrines primarily enshrine {{ill|Kami-musubi-no-Kami|ja|神皇産霊神|12=draft|12=draft}}.
* {{ill|Musubi Shrine (Tōgane City, Konumata)|ja|皇産靈神社 (東金市小沼田)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Konumata|ja|小沼田|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Tōgane City|ja|東金市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Chiba Prefecture|ja|千葉県|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Musubi Shrine (Tōgane City, Ōnumata)|ja|皇産靈神社 (東金市大沼田)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Ōnumata, Tōgane City, Chiba Prefecture. * {{ill|Yui Musubi Shrine|ja|油井皇産霊神社|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Yui|ja|油井|12=draft|12=draft}}, Tōgane City, Chiba Prefecture. * {{ill|Musubi Shrine (Sakura City)|ja|皇産霊神社 (佐倉市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Uchida|ja|内田|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Sakura City|ja|佐倉市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Chiba Prefecture. * {{ill|Musubi Shrine (Yachiyo City)|ja|皇産霊神社 (八千代市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Shimomarket|ja|下市場|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Yachiyo City|ja|八千代市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Chiba Prefecture. * {{ill|Musubi Shrine (Yotsukaidō City)|ja|皇産霊神社 (四街道市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Yotsukaidō City|ja|四街道市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Chiba Prefecture. * {{ill|Musubi Shrine (Kujūkuri Town)|ja|皇産靈神社 (九十九里町)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Kujūkuri Town|ja|九十九里町|12=draft|12=draft}}, Chiba Prefecture. * Musubi Shrine - Located in Hatake, {{ill|Kannami Town|ja|函南町|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Tagata District|ja|田方郡|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Shizuoka Prefecture|ja|静岡県|12=draft|12=draft}}. * Musubi Shrine - Located in {{ill|Oshino|ja|押野|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Nonoichi City|ja|野々市市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Ishikawa Prefecture|ja|石川県|12=draft|12=draft}}. Also known as {{ill|Takakōsanrei Shrine|ja|高皇産霊神社|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Musubi Shrine (Amagasaki City)|ja|皇産霊神社 (尼崎市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Amagasaki City|ja|尼崎市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Hyōgo Prefecture|ja|兵庫県|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Musubi Shrine (Kitakyūshū City)|ja|皇産霊神社 (北九州市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Moji Ward|ja|門司区|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Kitakyūshū City|ja|北九州市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Fukuoka Prefecture|ja|福岡県|12=draft|12=draft}}.
